udents of French cinema looking for examples of a director who could straddle the realms of the popular and the auteur.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aMotion picture producers and directorszFrancevBiography. 4aFilm and Media Studies 2019. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aAuteur.  aFrench cinema.  aJulien Duvivier.  aLiterary adaptation.  aNoir.  aPopular cinema.  aStardom.  aTheorising national cinema.1 aMcCann, Ben, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 2017 eBook-Packagez978311128281740uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978152610761940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526107619423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526107619/original  a978-3-11-128281-7  Manchester University Press 2017 eBook-Packageb2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles